                <note rend="inline" type="source">500.A 4e 1/65: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Schurman</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1924-05-09T15:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 9, 1924—3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>91. Your 123 May 7, 5 p.m. It is suggested that the objections anticipated by you
                    and your British colleague to the last paragraph of the draft note may be
                    obviated by substituting therefor the following: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“In making this communication, I am authorized to state that the Powers
                            concerned appreciate the importance of the situation and <pb facs="0634"
                                n="520" xml:id="pg_520"/> will continue, having regard to present
                            conditions in China, to give consideration to the question of bringing
                            into effect the provisions of the Washington Treaty.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <p>In view of the fact that the Chinese Government addressed separate notes, it is
                    believed preferable that the replies should likewise be made separately, though
                    so far as possible in identic language.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
